About OpenPNE3
==============

OpenPNE is an open source SNS Engine (social networking platform). It is a famous product in Japanese.

OpenPNE is born on 2005, and it used of over thirty-thousand websites now.

OpenPNE1 and OpenPNE2 is created by our original framework, but OpenPNE3 isn't so. We have rewritten OpenPNE from scratch for symfony, and it was released as OpenPNE3.

OpenPNE3 now get many features, a high maintainable and an extendable.
